stix:Indicator.indicator:Title: Malicious File Indicator
stix:Indicator.indicator:Description: According to a trusted third party, this is a 32-Bit "NPF.SYS" driver installed depending on host architechture. NPF.SYS is a WINPCAP driver used for packet capture utilities. Driver is installed if not present, or overwritten if an existing version is already present. Maps to Windows Service, "NETPLG"
